{"id":438,"date":"2017-01-03T00:40:21","date_gmt":"2017-01-03T05:40:21","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/achivion.grafitum.com\/portfolio\/itsonme-2-copy.html"},"modified":"2019-06-26T09:14:57","modified_gmt":"2019-06-26T13:14:57","slug":"socialtables","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/achievion.com\/portfolio\/socialtables.html","title":{"rendered":"Event Planning <span>SaaS<\/span>"},"content":{"rendered":"<div class=\"block-right\">\n<div class=\"project-info overview\">\n<h2>Client<\/h2>\n<p>Social Tables is a rapidly growing company that offers SaaS-based event planning software. Their top customers include Hilton, Hyatt, and Harvard.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"project-info challenge\">\n<h2>Objective<\/h2>\n<p>Design new Cloud-based infrastructure to improve overall system performance and user experience.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"project-info solution\">\n<h2>Solution<\/h2>\n<p>Achievion&#8217;s infrastructure and Cloud experts analyzed the ongoing system issues and realized that product support infrastructure relied on a single MySQL database server hosted by a 3rd party provider. We created a roadmap to shift their entire infrastructure to the AWS cloud and configure it for peak load scenarios using highly scalable AWS services.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"project-info result\">\n<h2>Result<\/h2>\n<p>The outcome was a resilient solution equipped to support 1000s of simultaneous user requests.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Social Tables is a rapidly growing company that offers SaaS-based event planning software.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":500,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[3],"tags":[78],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/achievion.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/438"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/achievion.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/achievion.com\/wp-js